{"tid":2148045,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣獨立遊戲Red Virus上架Steam","createTime":"2020-08-09T16:09:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T04:50:38.000Z","uid":274094,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8746868f4963af2944c0ca67b57cef92808c554f","tid":2148045,"uid":274094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T16:09:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WM4BKvm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWM4BKvm.jpg&h=dadf7a67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSteam <br />\n<a href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/1314250/Red_Virus/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F1314250%2FRed_Virus%2F&d=V6cANorTbu7KkBEK5B25YvolgVFqTZkzW3om5iGclzM%3D&h=d1a2912a\" target=\"_blank\">https://store.steampowered.com/app/1314250/Red_Virus/</a><br />\n<br />\n由台灣獨立開發者 Leonard H 製作的遊戲《赤毒》（Red Virus）昨（4）日在 Steam 與 ltch.lo 平台展開搶先體驗，定價為新台幣 188 元（目前九折 169 元中），根據作者本身表示，這款遊戲的目的是為了「傳遞一個訊息，告知全世界赤毒的危害。」<br />\n作品本身為一款 FPS 遊戲，提供多人和單人模式，多人模式可由玩家自行開房組隊，最多四人一起連線破關。從截圖與宣傳預告來看，嗯，大家應該都很清楚這所謂的敵人是誰，網友們看到紛紛回應：「看到遊戲畫面快笑死XDD」、「玻璃價格又要飆漲」、「應該很快就被進攻了<br />\n<br />\n官方預告<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Z7-V0FyylOQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZ7-V0FyylOQ&d=V6cANorTbu7KkBEK5B25YvolgVFqTZkzW3om5iGclzM%3D&h=399b28e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Z7-V0FyylOQ</a><br />\n<br />\n實機畫面<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/50WnAcHIBCQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F50WnAcHIBCQ&d=V6cANorTbu7KkBEK5B25YvolgVFqTZkzW3om5iGclzM%3D&h=792475c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/50WnAcHIBCQ</a><br />\n<br />\n（可能old news 隻驚幾日前係台灣紅左，但唔覺有人post）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de266b5e63dc3770c77aa85a70083ec1ea2aacb5","tid":2148045,"uid":274094,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T16:14:5